     "text": [
      "Contracts: 4,253 → 397  (kept 9.3%)\n",
      "  Calls    : 290\n",
      "  Puts     : 107\n",
      "  Expiries : 23\n",
      "\n",
      "Per-row rate / yield columns stamped by filter_chain_with_stats:\n",
      "  df[\"r\"] present : True  (range 3.591% – 4.134%)\n",
      "  df[\"q\"] present : True  (values: {'NVDA': '47.0000%'})\n",
